description:
Creates a Payload CMS 3.0 SingleRelationshipField configuration

Example:
```typescript
{
  name: 'singlerelationshipField',
  type: 'singlerelationship',
  required: true,
  label: 'Singlerelationship Field',
  // Custom validation example
  validate: (value, { siblingData, operation }) => {
    // Validation logic based on the value, sibling data, or operation
    if (operation === 'create' && !value) {
      return 'This field is required for new records';
    }
    return true;
  }
}
```

template:
{
  name: '{name}', // Database field name
  type: 'singlerelationship',
  label: 'Singlerelationship Field', // Label shown in the admin UI
  required: true,
  // Add field-specific properties here

  // Optional: Add custom validation
  validate: (value, { siblingData, operation }) => {
    // Custom validation logic based on the value, sibling data, or operation
    if (!value && operation === 'create') {
      return 'This field is required for new records';
    }
    return true; // Return true if valid
  },
  ...{rest}
}
